  div.container-fluid(style='padding-top:25px;')
    .row-fluid
      .span2
        .well.sidebar-nav
          ul.nav.nav-list
            li.nav-header Event
            li.active
              a(href="/") MaconMaps
            li
              a(href="https://maps.google.com/maps?saddr=Poplar+St,+Macon,+GA&daddr=Johnson+Ave,+Macon,+GA&hl=en&ll=32.834705,-83.64398&spn=0.020193,0.037937&sll=32.834957,-83.641019&sspn=0.020193,0.037937&geocode=FdIK9QEdheAD-w%3BFTD-9AEdWpMD-w&mra=dme&mrsp=0&sz=15&t=m&z=15", target="_blank") Directions
            
            li.nav-header Datasets
            li
              a(href="http://mta-mac.com/map.html", target="_blank") Buses
            li
              a(href="#") Parks
            li
              a(href="#", target="_blank") Housing

            li.nav-header Team Macon
            li
              a(href="http://codeforamerica.org") Code for America
            li
              a(href="http://knightfoundation.org") Knight Foundation
            li
              a(href="http://cityofmacon.net") City of Macon

        
      .span10
        img#backupimg(src="/images/MaconTiltShadow.png")
        .row-fluid
          .span12
            .well#eventpiece
              h1(style='font-size:30pt;') Macon Maps
              br
              h3 Middle Georgia's first mapping event
              br
              h3 Brought to you by&nbsp;
                a(href="http://codeforamerica.org") Code for America
              br
              a.btn.btn-primary(href="http://maconmaps.eventbrite.com") Join Us: September 20 @ 6PM
              br
              span Center for Collaborative Journalism, Mercer University
              br
              div(style="clear:both;")

        .row-fluid
          .span6
            h2 Objective: OpenStreetMap
            p
              h4 Code for America is opening data to make the best map of Macon, ever.
            p
              span When you edit&nbsp;
              a(href='http://www.openstreetmap.org/?lat=32.845&lon=-83.6348&zoom=14&layers=Q') OpenStreetMap
              span &nbsp;you're making a better map for all of us.
            p How did Apple catch up to Google and release their own maps this year?&nbsp;
              a(href="http://arstechnica.com/apple/2012/05/two-months-later-apple-acknowledges-use-of-openstreetmap-in-iphoto/") They used OpenStreetMap.
            p Craigslist is&nbsp;
              a(href="http://idealab.talkingpointsmemo.com/2012/08/craigslist-maps-test-openstreetmap.php") mapping your next apartment
              span &nbsp;on OpenStreetMap.
            p Foursquare uses OpenStreetMap&nbsp;
              a(href="http://foursquare.com") on their website
            p OpenStreetMap is even used to make&nbsp;
              a(href="http://softcities.net/") blankets and "mapkins".
     
          .span6
            h2 Neighborhoods
            p We've reached out to two Macon neighborhoods to help make maps that matter:
            p
              h4 College Hill
              span The College Hill Alliance supports business, art, and sports in the neighborhood surrounding Mercer University.
              br
              span Learn more at&nbsp;
              a(href='http://collegehillmacon.com/') CollegeHillMacon.com
            p
              h4 Lynmore Estates
              span Habitat for Humanity has built new homes and a Kaboom playground to revitalize a neighborhood in South Macon.
              br
              span Learn more at&nbsp;
              a(href="http://www.maconhabitat.org/current-building-projects") MaconHabitat.org

